Vibe Graphing Intent: Shadow Ops SaaS (Problem-Led Solutions)

Model Configuration:
- Build Model (Architect): Gemini 2.0 Flash
- Invoke Model (Worker): opencode:ollama

Design Intent:
Construct an autonomous pipeline for identifying SaaS opportunities through high-signal Reddit mining. 
The system will harvest pain points, qualify them as viable SaaS solutions (Problem-Led Solutions), 
and deliver tailored pitches via NotebookLM.

Structural Constraints (Topology):
START -> [B-Line_Hunter] -> [Diagnostic_Agent] -> [Solution_Architect] -> [Pitch_Agent] -> END
B-Line_Hunter: Scans Reddit (r/GrowthOperating, r/SaaS, etc.) for high-signal "Revenue Leaks" or "Operational Fragility."
Diagnostic_Agent: Performs automated audits on the harvested pain points to qualify market demand.
Solution_Architect: Synthesizes findings into a SaaS MVP Blueprint and generates the NotebookLM pitch asset.
Pitch_Agent: Executes targeted outreach and monitors for engagement triggers.

Data Contracts:
- PULL: skills/knowledge-base/references/memory_mesh/Zettels/SHADOW_OPS_WEAVE.md, skills/b_line_arsenal/SKILL.md
- PUSH: .brain/outputs/saas_mvp_blueprint.json, .mira/scores/pls_traction.json

Context Adapters:
- PathRAG: Access historical "Battle-Testing" logs from Reddit research.
- MCP: Utilize B-Line Arsenal tools and Neural Relay scripts.

Role Assignment:
- Hunter: ⚛️ First Principles + 🔬 Scientific Method
- Diagnostic: 🔬 Scientific Method + ⚙️ Pragmatic Application
- Architect: ✨ Creative Synthesis + 🤔 Philosophical Inquiry
- Pitch: ⚙️ Pragmatic Application + 🌑 The Dark Passenger
